Start spreading the news!🗞️🤑 20% sitewide + free gift with pruchases $45+!
 
 Offer ends at 11:59PM PST on 12/2/24. Valid only for online purchases made at herocosmetics.com. Purchase total must be $45+ before shipping and taxes in order to redeem the free gift. The gift with purchase is limited to one gift per customer and while supplies last. Deal cannot be applied to past purchases, combined with other coupons or discounts, subscriptions or redeemed for cash or merchandise credit. All discounts will be shown automatically on qualifying items in cart, no promo code needed.
